<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />How precious is your covenant faithfulness, God!</para>

<para style="q1">Humanity takes refuge under the shadow of your wings.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />They will be abundantly satisfied with the richness of the food of your house;</para>

<para style="q1">you will let them drink from the river of your precious blessings.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />For with you is the fountain of life;</para>

<para style="q1">in your light we will see light.</para>
